-mogura-card-thumb position-relative"><img class="mg-img-cover position-absolute h-100 w-100" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/11/7e207b493426ac756e8d7aa0391cbbea-kix.fnp6vz1je5vj-300x169.png"></div><div class="card-body mg-card-text p-2 p-lg-3"><h3 class="h6 mt-0 mw-0 mb-1 p-0 card-title mg-card-title mg-text-break-all text-dark font-weight-normal"> THE IDOLM@STER 的挑战项目“vα-liv”的目标是什么？ 《PROJECT IM@S vα-liv》制作人访谈</h3><div class="text-gray mg-mogura-card-excerpt mb-1 my-md-2">THE IDOLM@STER的新偶像项目“PROJECT IM@S vα-liv”于2023年4月启动。目前，Aika Akari、Uchuu Shusui和Retora这三名候选人正在该团体中，他们的目标是作为偶像“出道”。</div> <span class="badge badge-outline-live mg-mogura-card-badge px-2">VTuber</span> <span class="text-muted small ml-1">2023.11.16</span></div></div></div><h2>三人首次亮相的“876 Production”是什么？</h2><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/809e9b9e6657ff304de7ef049e47012f-kix.8dwbiza51g4b-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/809e9b9e6657ff304de7ef049e47012f-kix.8dwbiza51g4b-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/809e9b9e6657ff304de7ef049e47012f-kix.8dwbiza51g4b-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/809e9b9e6657ff304de7ef049e47012f-kix.8dwbiza51g4b-300x170.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/809e9b9e6657ff304de7ef049e47012f-kix.8dwbiza51g4b-768x435.webp 768w" width="1000" height="567" /></a><br /> （来自<a href="https://twitter.com/valiv_official/status/1774404142964052458" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PROJECT IM@S vα-liv 官方 X（前 Twitter）</a> ）</p><p>三位偶像候选人在《876制作》中出道的话题引起了《偶像大师》粉丝们的广泛关注。这是因为“876 Production”是2009年面向任天堂DS<strong>发行的</strong>游戏<strong>“</strong> <a href="https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ds/software/vimj/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>偶像大师亲爱的明星”</strong></a>中出现的机构名称。</p><p><strong>日高爱</strong>、<strong>水谷绘里</strong>和<strong>秋月亮</strong>属于 876 Pro。这些偶像也出现在其他作品中，秋月亮也被称为秋月律子的弟弟。 876 Pro 与 Haruka Amami 等人所属的 765 Pro 有联系，但在 DS 之后的发展受到限制。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[我尝试唱歌]“HELLO!!” - Dearly Stars [由 vα-liv 翻唱]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zxBftixd3Gk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>事实上，Vα-LIV的偶像候选人一年前也翻唱了Dearly Stars的一首歌曲，可以说当时就已经暗示了这种联系。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/809e9b9e6657ff304de7ef049e47012f-kix.7qf7hf17xa6c-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/809e9b9e6657ff304de7ef049e47012f-kix.7qf7hf17xa6c-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/809e9b9e6657ff304de7ef049e47012f-kix.7qf7hf17xa6c-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/809e9b9e6657ff304de7ef049e47012f-kix.7qf7hf17xa6c-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/809e9b9e6657ff304de7ef049e47012f-kix.7qf7hf17xa6c-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>与本次合作公告一起，还发布了社长石川稔的致辞。我好奇的不仅是三人未来的偶像活动，还有876 Pro是否会重启。</p><p> ©久书田敏之 THE IDOLM@STER <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2122.png" alt="™" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> &amp; ©万代南梦宫娱乐公司<br />（参考） <a href="https://twitter.com/valiv_official/status/1774403943122260404" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方X（原Twitter）</a> 、<a href="https://idolmaster-official.jp/news/01_11156" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方新闻</a>、 <a href="https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ds/software/vimj/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nintendo DS官方页面</a></p><p>近日<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/project-imas-v%ce%b1-liv-876/">，偶像大师培养计划“vα-liv”三名成员通过了期末考试！他所属的“876 Pro”首先</a>在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.m