938 <p> 3D模型运动捕获工具“网络摄像头运动捕获”具有使用网络摄像头的Furt跟踪功能（Beta版本）的实现。结果，我将整个身体的运动与Avatar和Vtuber Active同步[…]</p><p>帖子VTUBER工具“<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">网络摄像头</a><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/webcam-motion-capture-full-tracking/">运动捕获”支持使用网络摄像头的完整跟踪</a>。</p> ]>;]] </description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p> 3D模型运动捕获工具“<a href="https://webcammotioncapture.info/ja/index.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">网络摄像头运动捕获</a>”具有使用网络摄像头的Furt跟踪功能（Beta版本）的实现。这使您可以将整个身体运动与头像同步，并将其用于VTUBER活动。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.fylgof9r4e69-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.fylgof9r4e69-1024x386.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.fylgof9r4e69-1024x386.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.fylgof9r4e69-300x113.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.fylgof9r4e69-768x289.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.fylgof9r4e69-1536x579.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.fylgof9r4e69-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="386" /></a></p><p>该试用版目前可免费使用（官方版本可每月使用199日元）。完整的3D模型可以使用网络摄像头运行多少？我实际上尝试了。</p><h2>轻松体验Furt跟踪</h2><p>“网络摄像头动作捕获”是一种跟踪工具，其AI于2021年发布。 3D模型的上半身（头部运动，表情等）和手动跟踪的特征是一个功能。</p><p>它还支持使用iOS终端面ID实现的面部跟踪应用程序，还可以与分发工具“ <a href="https://obsproject.com/ja" target="_blank" rel="noopener">obs Studio</a> ”结合使用在YouTube和其他视频网站上实时发行。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="使用手跟踪，faceid和waidayo的完美水槽！ -EBCAM运动捕获1.5.0发布" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/M3HujhnF76M?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>通常，使用全身跟踪的3D模型时，使用了专用跟踪器，例如“ Mocopi”，“ Haritorax”，“ Vive Tracker”。这些设备价格昂贵（从数万日元开始），但是“网络摄像头运动捕获”整体跟踪功能与市售的网络摄像机兼容，因此您可以轻松地使用“ Fultra”。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.voo32jd426aw-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.voo32jd426aw-1024x626.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.voo32jd426aw-1024x626.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.voo32jd426aw-300x183.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.voo32jd426aw-768x470.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.voo32jd426aw-jpg.webp 1176w" width="1024" height="626" /></a><br /> （演示版的主屏幕。您可以在官方版本中删除菜单和示例文本）</p><p>下载应用程序并启动应用程序后，主屏幕上的“网络摄像头运动捕获”是“跟踪模式”列，您可以通过切换到整个身体来使用它。我们不需要设置单个网络摄像机的设置，但被使用。有必要在反射腰部的位置设置一个摄像头（位置）。</p><p>当我真正尝试过它时，只要我站在网上摄像头的前面，我就可以使用完整的跟踪功能而没有任何问题。不仅上半身的整体运动，而且手指运动（手动跟踪）的功能牢固。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.3atc689j7egh-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.3atc689j7egh-1024x621.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.3atc689j7egh-1024x621.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.3atc689j7egh-300x182.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.3atc689j7egh-768x466.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.3atc689j7egh-jpg.webp 1190w" width="1024" height="621" /></a><br /> （和平的迹象也被很好地认可）</p><p>印象是，下半身的运动可以在分布中充分使用。在我的环境中，起初它有些不稳定，但是即使超出了摄像机范围<strong>，即使既不反射膝盖在相机中反射到脚部，也可以固定脚部位置</strong>”，即使超过了相机范围”。四肢不再是“飞行（ *朝意外的方向移动）”。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.py5u5jyxmgzj-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.py5u5jyxmgzj-1024x614.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.py5u5jyxmgzj-1024x614.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.py5u5jyxmgzj-300x180.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.py5u5jyxmgzj-768x461.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.py5u5jyxmgzj-jpg.webp 1192w" width="1024" height="614" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.xplrjg7amzqs-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.xplrjg7amzqs-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 731px) 100vw, 731px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.xplrjg7amzqs-jpg.webp 731w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.xplrjg7amzqs-300x293.webp 300w" width="731" height="714" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.gk12a9feddcz-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.gk12a9feddcz-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 553px) 100vw, 553px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.gk12a9feddcz-jpg.webp 553w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.gk12a9feddcz-266x300.webp 266w" width="553" height="623" /></a><br /> （印象，当此复选框打开时，跟踪是稳定的）</p><p>我觉得可以在聊天分布中没有任何问题的情况下使用这种准确性。如果您可以固定较大的空间，则似乎可以用于移动身体的游戏中，例如Nintendo Switch的“ Ring Fit Adventure”。</p><p>但是，根据角度的不同，即使只有一条腿在移动，两条腿也可以同时移动。移动身体似乎很重要，以便软件侧可以轻松识别运动，或穿易于识别腿部的衣服。</p><p>此外，这次我使用了Logitech的“ C270 HD Web摄像头”进行测试，但是由于它与缩放不兼容，因此“拆卸”范围有一个限制。如果您使用更广阔的视角（宽角兼容）相机，则可以进一步扩展跟踪范围。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.ma729mikc38b-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.ma729mikc38b-1024x624.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.ma729mikc38b-1024x624.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.ma729mikc38b-300x183.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.ma729mikc38b-768x468.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/c74b1e171de49abf6200a1bdb49a80a9-kix.ma729mikc38b-jpg.webp 1184w" width="1024" height="624" /></a></p><p>除Windows版本外，MACOS版本中还提供了“网络摄像头运动捕获”演示版本。如果您想使用化身制作3D模型和视频，为什么不尝试一次呢？</p><p><a href="https://webcammotioncapture.info/ja/beta.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>单击此处下载演示版本“网络摄像头运动捕获”</strong></a> （Beta版本）</p><p>写作：ibun</p><p>帖子VTUBER工具“<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">网络摄像头</a><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/webcam-motion-capture-full-tracking/">运动捕获”支持使用网络摄像头的完整跟踪</a>。</p> ]>;]] </content:encoded><media:content height="180" m